{"tid":555972,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"17歲女生柴灣街頭遇險    遭狂徒迎面掩嘴","createTime":"2018-02-10T04:57:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-10T06:14:25.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"517d8d40463531c25ba165ba33f7b109e777ed5e","tid":555972,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T04:57:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180210/large/1518238122_e743.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180210%2Flarge%2F1518238122_e743.jpg&h=1b143f14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n柴灣出現掩嘴狂徒。昨日中午12時左右，一名17歲女生，行經新廈街時，迎面一名南亞漢突然伸手過來想掩她的口。女生大驚，撥開後慌忙逃跑，返回附近的學校報警求助。警方接報後在附近搜索，但沒有發現，列遊蕩案，交由東區刑事調查隊跟進。"},{"pid":"a9c627e35eea6b29569be69cebd236235d39c93c","tid":555972,"uid":106336,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T05:00:03.000Z","msg":"點解永遠都係南亞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f6a67d764cc27b82ca8050c5023a722ced65901","tid":555972,"uid":123711,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T05:00:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"be138453708b25e40504594b8237d93c7a278970","tid":555972,"uid":19908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T05:10:20.000Z","msg":"香港就黎變印度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b73e710cf5dec0ee6f68a47ed4938caed107a479","tid":555972,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T05:13:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">南亞漢</span>"},{"pid":"49df6f0f5e57ac94c7cbd73805abbc85b87bcf7f","tid":555972,"uid":96871,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T05:18:07.000Z","msg":"其實張超雄收左幾多錢放班垃圾黎入浸香港？"},{"pid":"2c81b09ea83f9a3c74b16cc9bc0b84445f025810","tid":555972,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T05:18:18.000Z","msg":"@UST 南亞仔"},{"pid":"